sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { InfoContainter, InfoWrapper, InfoRow, Column1, Column2, TextWrapper, TopLine, Heading, Subtitle, ImgWrap, Img } from './InfoElements'; const InfoSection = ({lightBg, id, imgStart, topLine, lightText, headline, darkText, description, img, alt, primary, dark, dark2}) => { return ( <> {topLine} {headline} {description} ) }; export default InfoSection;
